# D.A. Palmquist Portfolio

## 🎨 Professional Portfolio for Comic Book Artist & AI Pioneer

A cutting-edge full-stack portfolio showcasing the creative work of Peter D. Allen under the pseudonym D.A. Palmquist, featuring the Principia multimedia franchise (rebranded from Frontier: 2170).

### ✨ Key Features

- **🎧 AI Audiobook Player** - Functional audio player with ElevenLabs AI narration
- **📚 Published Works** - Showcase of Frontier: 2170 graphic novel series
- **🎨 Original Concept Art** - Character designs and world-building visuals
- **🤖 AI Integration** - Demonstrates cutting-edge generative AI workflows
- **📱 Mobile Responsive** - Perfect experience across all devices
- **⚡ Dark Futuristic Theme** - Electric Amber accent color scheme

### 🏗️ Tech Stack

**Frontend:**
- React 19 with TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS for styling
- Shadcn/UI component library
- Axios for API communication
- React Router for navigation

**Backend:**
- FastAPI (Python)
- MongoDB with Motor (async driver)
- Pydantic for data validation
- Contact form handling
- Audio interaction analytics

**Deployment:**
- Vercel for hosting
- MongoDB Atlas for database
- Custom domain: da-palmquist-portfolio.com

### 🎯 Portfolio Sections

1. **Hero Section** - Professional introduction
2. **About** - Artist background and mission
3. **Skills** - Technical, Creative, and Business competencies  
4. **Experience** - Detailed work history
5. **Projects** - Featured works with real Amazon book covers
6. **Principia Deep Dive** - Interactive AI audiobook demonstration
7. **Contact** - Functional contact form with validation

### 🚀 Live Demo

Visit: [https://da-palmquist-portfolio.com](https://da-palmquist-portfolio.com)

